<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-67-0058 </DOCNO><TEXT>Science Applications International Corporation (SAIC) has undertaken anextensive international data collection project that includes surveyingall wind turbine and component manufacturers, and independently identifyingthe wind turbines installed by country. Information is being collectedin four basic areas: company descriptions, wind turbine specifications,wind turbine shipments and applications. The authors present a broadoverview of windfarm applications for the world market over the nextfive years. As the California market stabilizes, it is of value to identifywhere the growth will be and the characteristics of this growth. Alsothey provide an overview of the U.S. market.</TEXT></DOC>